Support Services


































In addition to our medical services, we provide support services that address your full range of physical, emotional, and spiritual needs. These services are also available at the Stanford Neuroscience Health Center for your convenience.
Onsite offerings include:

Exercise classes
Nutrition counseling
Patient education
Social work
Support groups









