Neuro Kinetics Inc: Company Profile - Bloomberg



































































  









Feedback


























neuro kinetics inc
Private Company









Company Profile
Sector: Health Care
Industry: Medical Equipment & Devices
Sub-Industry: Health Care Supplies
Neuro Kinetics, Inc. was founded in 2002. The company's line of business includes the manufacturing of medical, surgical, ophthalmic, and veterinary instruments and apparatus.




